iv></a><a id=\"zulfiqar\" class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 border border-emerald-100 hover:border-emerald-300 group hover:-translate-y-1 block\" href=\"/names/islamic/zulfiqar\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">Zulfiqar</h3><span class=\"inline-block mt-2 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">Arabic</span></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-emerald-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-4\">&quot;<!-- -->Cleaver<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Origin:</span><span>Arabic</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Lucky Number:</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full font-bold\">3</span></div></div></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-emerald-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What are the most popular Islamic boy names?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">The most popular Islamic boy names include Muhammad, Ahmad, Ali, Hassan, Hussain, Umar, Usman, Bilal, Yusuf, Ibrahim, Hamza, and Khalid. These names have deep roots in Islamic history and Arabic tradition, making them timeless choices for Muslim families worldwide.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-emerald-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">How do I choose an Islamic name for my baby boy?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">When choosing an Islamic name for your baby boy, consider the Arabic meaning, origin, and whether it has Quranic reference. Names with positive meanings like &#x27;Praised&#x27;, &#x27;Wise&#x27;, &#x27;Merciful&#x27;, or &#x27;Eternal&#x27; are highly recommended in Islamic tradition.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-emerald-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What Islamic boy names mean &#x27;Praised&#x27;?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Several Islamic boy names carry the meaning &#x27;Praised&#x27;, including Muhammad and Ahmad. These names express gratitude and are beloved choices among Muslim families worldwide.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center\">Explore More Names</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-rose-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/islamic/girl-names\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Islamic Girl Names</h3><p class=\"text-pink-100 text-sm\">Browse 139+ Muslim girl names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/names/religion/islamic/1\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">All Islamic Names</h3><p class=\"text-emerald-100 text-sm\">Discover 25,000+ Islamic names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to